      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start, really captures the atmosphere. To make the tension even more realistic, I need to describe the people moving through the scene. I don't want it to feel generic, so can you add some details about the types of people hanging out on these corners or walking through the shadows? Like, what are they wearing, what are they doing, and what kind of \"vibe\" do they give off that makes the protagonist feel like they shouldn't be there?",
